      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of BMW\u2019s high-revving S54 platform. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six delivers exceptional throttle response via individual throttle bodies, with the VANOS system recently serviced for optimal variable valve timing. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis has been inspected for subframe integrity and features refreshed bushings to maintain the sharp turn-in characteristics of the original M-tuned suspension. This is a driver-spec machine with excellent compression and a clean valvetrain, ready for the purist who values engineering over aesthetics.",
